      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014pristine condition, inside and out! I've babied this car since day one, so it's looking flawless and drives like a dream. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
