      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E92 M3, a definitive example of the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8 era. This specimen features the 4.0-liter powerplant with individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio, delivering linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The six-speed manual gearbox offers crisp gate engagement, paired with a perfectly preserved M-Variable Differential Lock for optimal lateral traction. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, with the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system providing immediate valve-rate adjustments. Every mechanical interface, from the rod bearings to the subframe mounting points, has been fastidiously maintained to ensure peak harmonic balance. This is a concours-level vehicle with original paint depth and an interior free of delamination or bolster fatigue.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "One owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint. Interior flawless. Full service records included. Mechanically perfect.",
      "price": 48500.0,
