    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2021 BMW M2 Competition is a true collector's piece, maintained in absolute showroom condition. Finished in Hockenheim Silver Metallic, the paint is protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating and shows zero swirls, chips, or imperfections. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with full documentation included. The interior still retains that new-car scent, with the Dakota leather seats and carbon fiber trim appearing untouched. Garaged in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather, this vehicle is mechanically flawless and visually indistinguishable from a brand-new model. For the buyer who demands perfection, this is the finest example currently available.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
